HEADWORD: Twelvemonth
<hw>Twelve"month</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A year which
consists of twelve calendar months.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I shall laugh at this a <qex>twelvemonth</qex> hence.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Twelvepence</ent>⟦br⟧
